===Noun===
'''peroxide'''

#{{chemistry}} a [[divalent]] [[radical]] or [[anion]]  containing two [[oxygen]] [[atom]]s linked by a [[covalent bond]]; any substance containing this group which yields [[hydrogen peroxide]] when treated with an [[acid]]
# [[hydrogen peroxide]], especially an [[aqueous]] [[solution]]

